      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
           05  k-fix                      pic  x(08) value
                     "sfonum  "                                       .
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
      *        * Componente variabile : 10 caratteri                   *
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
           05  k-var.
               10  k-scl-ann              pic  9(03)                  .
               10  filler                 pic  x(07)                  .
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
      *        * Contatore numero frammenti                            *
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
           05  k-cnf                      pic  9(02)                  .

